node.text: Casually elegant & designed for entertaining by architect Alyson Sailer! POOL home w/stunning golf course views, soaring ceilings, walnut floors, 3 fireplaces & window wall overlooking resort backyard w/covered porch, fireplace, outdoor kitchen, waterfall & pool. Lux kitchen w/prof appliances & caterers pantry w/warming drawers, ice machine, wine cooler, prep sink & add'l dishwasher. Primary retreat & guest suite on main, ensuites, bunk rm & media up. PLUS 600 sq/ft unfinished flex space!

node.title: Entertainer’s Dream in The Grove… with pool!

node.text: Stunning home in popular Cartwright Close...updated & move in ready! This home was built in 2017 by Trace Construction & has been renovated w/ gorgeous finishes throughout. Outdoor entertaining will be a dream on your large covered porch w/ fireplace overlooking a gorgeous salt water pool and luxurious backyard. Presented by @lctteam_parks: 615.300.8285.

node.text:
Old world luxury meets modern times! Charming English Tudor completely restored with newly added addition in 2015. This estate is truly one of a kind! Features in this home are unique, like the original carriage house now used as a wine tasting room. Situated among mature trees on nearly an acre with plunge pool and hot tub. Fabulous location convenient to everything!

Listing Courtesy of Benchmark Realty, LLC, Anne Ruark (615.210.6966) #luxuryrealestate #luxuryhomemagazine #luxuryhomes #luxurynashville #nashvilleluxury #nashvilleluxuryhomes

node.title: English Tudor in heart of Nashville- Now Available!

node.text:
This 14,096 sq ft home in Murfreesboro features a western elegant feel on 90 acres with 9 stall horse barn & 2BR + 2BA apartment & riding arena. 30+ rooms comprise a cinema rm, full bar, lounges and dining areas, & spacious kitchen, w/ custom stone and woodwork throughout. Luxury master bdr & bath look over pool w/ waterfall & pavilion. Each bdr has own full bath. Dance studio & fitness room tie in to large storage spaces. This is a one of a kind home unlike almost any other in the mid-state.  WELCOME TO WHAT IS PERHAPS, MIDDLE TENNESSEE'S MOST THOUGHTFULLY DESIGNED, WELL-CONSTRUCTED, AND METICULOUSLY PLANNED CUSTOM HOMES AVAILABLE TODAY. JUST MINUTES FROM NASHVILLE IN MURFREESBORO, TENNESSEE, THIS IMPRESSIVE 14,096 SQUARE FOOT HOME AND HORSE ARENA ARE THE CENTERPIECES OF A 90-ACRE, WELL-GROOMED PROPERTY. THIS IS A HOME BUILT FOR THE UTMOST IN LIVING AND ENTERTAINING AT THE HIGHEST LEVEL. IT IS A GRAND ESTATE OVERFLOWING WITH SOUTH WESTERN CHARM, WORLD-CLASS AMENITIES, AND UNIQUE DESIGN ELEMENTS AROUND EVERY CORNER. IT IS A PLACE TO FIND RESPITE AND PRIVACY WHILE ENJOYING LIFE AND NATURE TO ITS FULLEST. Presented by @danmcewen @mcewengroup 931.626.0241. 
#FivePeppersFarm #LuxuryHomeMagazine

node.text: A mere two blocks from Historic Franklin and all it has to offer including Retail, culinary, and cultural amenities of Main Street. Experience one level living with a next level lifestyle. Spacious living in each residence (2400-4200 SF), with luxury kitchens and owners suites, fenced dog walk, underground parking, conditioned storage rooms, and zero exterior maintenance. Brought to market by the developer of The Brownstones. Contact Bernie Butler today: 615.419.6933. #LuxuryHomeMagazine #TheArlington #HistoricFranklin #Concierge #LuxuryLockandLeave

node.title: The Arlington- One level Luxury Living in the heart of Historic Franklin

node.text:
Luxury Home Magazine is proud to partner with Luxury Homes of Tennessee for an exclusive broker open presented by Nathan Throneberry, tomorrow from 12-2pm. You're invited to an amazing afternoon of gourmet food by Five Senses, guided tours of this sprawling property, & one lucky guest will win a full page ad in an LHM Edition of your choice!

Sited just south of Nashville, this family compound has over 200 recreational acres, 21,000 square feet of total space, and overlooks the breathtaking Pine Creek with two private waterfalls over 55' tall and 39' wide! 

Email joinus@homestenn.com for gate code.

node.title: Broker Open at Pine Creek Falls

node.text:
Modern meets Classic in the heart of Green Hills! 5 Bedrooms 5.5 Bathrooms including 2 Main Floor Bedrooms with en suites PLUS an office. Massive open floor plan with designer elements to make you swoon. 48" Viking Range and 60" Electrolux Refrigerator/Freezer. Vaulted master suite that opens to the covered back patio. 3 car garage and double rec room / game room. This fabulous new home sits 160' from the street with a private drive and mature trees! Must See! JUST COMPLETED! Presented by @martinlovelace @jasonahlbrandt @lovelaceahlbrandtteam @benchmarkrealtytn.  Martin: 615.618.7232. 
Jason: 615.306.9688.

node.title: Modern Meets Classic in heart of Green Hills!

node.text: Beautiful Equestrian Estate, 27+ acres, features over 5250 sq ft home plus 920sq ft guest house, detached 3 car garage with 1600 sq ft apartment above garage. Numerous outbuildings, 60x80 hay barn, New 40x60 VENUE Barn with bathroom, concrete flooring, covered porch & tack room,3 stalls. In addition there are 5 fenced, pastures with run-in shelters/water, pond on back of property & large riding arena. Remote control front gate to property. Truly a gem in Spring Hill city limits. Listing Courtesy of VILLAGE, Barbara Hood (615.957.6019)
